text:
Reference page
In the _quarto.yml file, to specify the path to a custom template place it here:
pkgsite: 
  reference:
    template: "path to the template"
Here are the contents of the Quarto document used as the default:
---
title: "{{{{notitle.title}}}}"
execute:
  eval: true
  freeze: true
---

## {{{{notitle.alias}}}}

{{{{title.description}}}}

{{{{title.format}}}}

{{{{title.usage}}}}

{{{{title.arguments}}}}

{{{{title.details}}}}

{{{{title.section}}}}

{{{{title.value}}}}

{{{{title.note}}}}

{{{{title.examples}}}}

{{{{title.seealso}}}}

{{{{title.author}}}}

Examples

library(pkgsite)
example_pkg &lt;- system.file("example", package = "pkgsite")
rd_to_list("rd_to_list.Rd", project = example_pkg)
